*Ubistva* su se uvećala u poslednjih nekoliko godina. (Murders have increased in the last few years.)

Mnogi su ljudi optuženi za *ubistva*. (Many people have been accused of murders.)

U gradu je bilo nekoliko *ubistava* u poslednje vreme. (There have been several murders in the city lately.)

Sud je osudio osumnjičenog za *ubistva*. (The court has convicted the suspect of murder.)

Nadležne službe tragaju za počiniocem *ubistva*. (The authorities are searching for the perpetrator of the murder.)